Introduction

Yoo Shi-ah, also known as YooA, is the Main Dancer, Lead Vocalist, and Face of the girl group Oh My Girl under WM Entertainment.

She debuted as a member of OH MY GIRL on April 21, 2015, with the group's self-titled mini album.

YooA was, alongside other 6 female idols, in the “Idol Drama Operation Team” TV program and they created a 7 members girl group, called Girls Next Door. She is best known for her dancing skills and she would often appear in dancing programs such as "Hit the Stage" (2016).

In November 2016, she debuted in the Inkigayo project group, Sunny Girls, with the single, "Taxi".

On September 8, 2020, YooA made her solo debut with the mini album titled "Bon Voyage"
